name: Eric McCarthy
review: Have been attending church here since 1985, when my father was stationed at HAAF. Always feel welcome especially when I returned with my family after my military service was done.

name: Johnna Quick
review: They had a fundraiser,  with crafts,  and bbq, found  some  very vintage  post cards, great  prices.  And also some sweets.

name: Jen 818
review: I grew up at this church. It's like home away from hom. Unfortunately, the congression is growing smaller by the day and really needs a better promoter.

name: Ken O'Brien
review: Attended an event there.  Good space for our group. Thanks for letting us meet there.

name: Kisha Parrott
review: My most favorite polling center. Always enough staff & the wait is never long.

name: Bruce Riner
review: There for an Eagle Board of Review.
